Step 1 - Definition of line chart
Line chart is a chart in which the data is displayed as a series of the data points which are called the Markers and there markers are connected by a straight 
line segments.

Note - The dataset that we are going to use is "AirBnb" data in our previous video "How to make a Stacked column chart" we have given a detailed explanation 
about the dataset.



Step 2 - What output we are expecting?
So, we want to see the "Apartment prices according to neighbourhood".

Step 3 - Drag and Drop the columns
Drag and drop the "Neighbourhood" column onto the task window and do the same thing with "Price" column

Step 4 - Make line chart
So for making line chart we have to the visualization pane and from there select "line chart" which will convert the default chart into line chart
